*Zauzeta* sam preko vikenda. (I am busy this weekend.)
Ona je *zauzeta* sa svojim poslom. (She is busy with her work.)
On je *zauzet* svojim obavezama. (He is busy with his duties.)
Nema vremena da bude *zauzet* sada. (There is no time to be busy now.)
Ona je pre *zauzeta* da učestvuje. (She is too busy to participate.)
Neke stvari će biti *zauzete* zauvek. (Some things will be busy forever.)